The Adventures of Superman #452
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  March 1989

Writer:  Dan Jurgens and Jerry Ordway (plot assist)
Penciller:  Dan Jurgens
Inker:  Dennis Janke
Colorist:  Glenn Whitmore
Letterer:  John Costanza
Cover Artist:  Jerry Ordway

"Superman in Exile" part 4, continued from Superman v2 #29. Did the town of Trudeau, South Dakota die from mass suicide...or murder? Only the Word-Bringer knows for sure, and Superman will learn the answer if it's the last thing he does. Continued in Superman v2 #30.

Thanks goes to DreamGirl for this release.
